Comment: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:35.26,ZWDB,,0,0,0,,明白
Comment: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:41.94,ZWDB,,0,0,0,,上吧
Comment: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:43.18,ZWDB,,0,0,0,,是
Comment: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.89,ZWDB,,0,0,0,,诶 你们真狡猾
