Comment: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:09.88,ZWDB,,0,0,0,,诶
Comment: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:29.32,ZWDB,,0,0,0,,狂 狂暴补师
Comment: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:48.10,ZWDB,,0,0,0,,好了 接下来就是重头戏了
Comment: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:49.10,ZWDB,,0,0,0,,我们上
Comment: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:50.54,ZWDB,,0,0,0,,去打倒BOSS
